<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-338] Unable to disable assertions (-da)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-338</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m unable to disable assertions while running tests with the surefire plugin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have product &quot;assert1&quot; with a code with &quot;assert false&quot; (this always throws an AssertionError when assertions are enabled).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I use the code in assert2 in a unit-test and it &lt;b&gt;always&lt;/b&gt; throws an assertion error with surefire 2.3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &amp;lt;build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;plugins&amp;gt;    &lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-surefire-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;!-- emi: forcing version to avoid ignoring of -da --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;!-- &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;2.1.3&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt; --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;pertest&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;argLine&amp;gt;-da&amp;lt;/argLine&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;                    &amp;lt;childDelegation&amp;gt;false&amp;lt;/childDelegation&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/plugins&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/build&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can play with various values for forkMode and childDelegation with no luck.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The only working way is forcing the version to 2.1.33 and with the above settings (pertest forkmode, false childDelegation).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a zip with 2 projects. Trying to run mvn test on assert2 will throw an assertion error except if forcing the surefire version to 2.1.3.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
